meanings: (때·얼룩 등이) come out, wash out, be removed
(패배하다) lose, be defeated, be beaten, suffer a defeat
(물건을 등에) carry[have, take] sth on one's back
(얼룩 등이) be[get] stained (with), be smudged (with), be[get] spotted (with)
